the difficulty of accomplishing a move to option A later

2791
02:46:19.158 --> 02:46:22.938
while trying to find a superintendent to execute that

2792
02:46:22.958 --> 02:46:23.668
reconfiguration?

2793
02:46:28.418 --> 02:46:31.378
And I'd just like to say that if we don't choose option A, and instead we just

2794
02:46:31.458 --> 02:46:33.458
redistrict on top of taking away

2795
